      "body" : "Through chainparams it pulls in almost all the implementation files.\r\n\r\nThe only way to solve this would be to make util no longer depend on chainparams, or split up util into a part for the rpc client and a part for the server (after all, the rpc client doesn't even need the network-specific directory or any other part of util.cpp that depends on the chain params). ",
      "created_at" : "2013-10-12T22:03:33Z",
